Kopete, The KDE Messenger
Duncan Mac-Vicar Prett <duncan@kdedevelopers.net>
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Kopete is a IM client being designed to be modular and plugin based.

It requires the KDE Desktop, version 3 or higher.

Currently, the  supported protocol plugins are MSN, ICQ, AIM, IRC and
Jabber. Yahoo! support is currently under development and expected
to stabilise soon.

The Kopete developers can be contacted on our mailing list,
kopete-devel@kde.org.

Enjoy!

